description: I was walking around Prague suburbs looking for a catch when I saw this young looking guy playing with a toy car. At first, I was interested in the car because it drove really fast in the snow. I started talking to the guy and found out that he was not some boy playing with a toy. He was an 18 years old student. Quite a cutie. I didn´t waste any time and started giving him various naughty offers. He wasn´t very comfortable about it but needed money. Student´s life isn´t easy. Not even when you live at your parents. Fortunately, they weren´t home so we could enjoy the comfort and warmth of their apartment. We didn´t have much time so I had to act quickly. The parents were on the way and they would had been upset to see their youngest son fulfilling my every dirty wish.
title: Czech Hunter 335
